title: Call of Duty & United Offensive Cracked SP & Online
description:
Call Of Duty with Call Of Duty UO expantion with cracked online play. Version 1.4/1.41 No install required (Updated version with more servers and players)


1. First run the Call Of Duty MPSettings .reg file to load the correct multiplayer game settings to your computer(Important otherwise multiplayer wont work).




2. If you want to play call Of Duty UO online multiplayer browse the Call of Duty folder and lunch CoDUOMP.exe Wen the game starts select a server form the main menu or refresh favorites in the server browser. (most players and servers)


3. If you want to play call Of Duty 1 online multiplayer browse the Call of Duty folder and lunch CoDMP.exe Wen the game starts select a server form the main menu or refresh favorites in the server browser.


4. To Play call of duty 1 singleplayer browse the Call of Duty folder and lunch CoDSP.exe


5. To Play call of duty united offensive singleplayer browse the Call of Duty folder and lunch CoDUOSP.exe


OBS!: If you get an error "can not write to hunkusage.dat", this is fixed by deleting this gamefile /main/HUNKUSAGE.DAT for cod 1
for united offensive /uo/HUNKUSAGE.DAT
